# Project Structure

Canonical map: [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md). Details: [docs/README.md](mdc:docs/README.md).

## Apps

- [apps/server](mdc:apps/server/src/server.ts) — Express API (module-first)
- [apps/web](mdc:apps/web/app/layout.tsx) — Next.js App Router
- [apps/worker](mdc:apps/worker/src/index.ts) — background jobs
- [apps/cli](mdc:apps/cli/AGENTS.md) — scaffold CLI

## Packages

- [packages/trpc](mdc:packages/trpc/src/index.ts) — API contract (re-exports server router)
- [packages/store](mdc:packages/store/prisma/schema.prisma) — Prisma
- [packages/auth](mdc:packages/auth/src/index.ts) — Better Auth
- [packages/backend-common](mdc:packages/backend-common/AGENTS.md) — env, Redis, logger
- [packages/ui](mdc:packages/ui/src) — shared UI

## Tooling

- [turbo.json](mdc:turbo.json)
- [toolings/typescript-config](mdc:toolings/typescript-config)
- [toolings/scripts](mdc:toolings/scripts/AGENTS.md)

## Conventions

- Web calls the API via `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`; do not import server-only modules in `apps/web`.
- Deploy API with Render Blueprint ([render.yaml](mdc:render.yaml)), not ad-hoc Native Bun from repo root.
